OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FITV News' Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,7,Freports from the US where King Charles
OL,8,Fwill be arriving for a historic state
OL,9,Fvisit
OL,11,FKing Charles and Queen Camilla have
OL,12,Farrived in Washington DC for a four-
OL,13,Fday visit aimed at marking the 250th
OL,14,Fanniversary of American independence
OL,15,Fand strengthening the special UK-US
OL,16,Frelationship.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
