OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777546977
OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FThat relationship has been under
OL,7,Fserious strain in recent months, with
OL,8,FUS President Donald Trump lambasting
OL,9,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer and other
OL,10,FEuropean allies over their reluctance
OL,11,Fto get involved in the war with Iran.
OL,13,FThe visit is the most important
OL,14,Fforeign trip of the King's reign so
OL,15,Ffar, but now has the added element of
OL,16,Fsecurity concerns following a shooting
OL,17,Fat the White House Correspondents'
OL,18,FAssociation dinner on Saturday evening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
