CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777546977
OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FThe historic visit, the King's first
OL,7,Fto the US as monarch, will mark the
OL,8,Fstart of celebrations marking the
OL,9,F250th anniversary of the signing of
OL,10,Fthe Declaration of Independence, which
OL,11,Ffollowed forces led by George
OL,12,FWashington's defeat of King George
OL,13,FIII's army.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
