OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777546977
OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FUS First Lady Melania Trump has led
OL,7,Fthe preparations for the state visit,
OL,8,Fand highlights include Charles'
OL,9,Faddress to both houses of Congress and
OL,10,Fthe royal couple marking the 25th
OL,11,Fanniversary of the September 11
OL,12,Fterrorist attacks that brought down
OL,13,FNew York's Twin Towers.
OL,15,FIt is understood that following the
OL,16,Fshooting in Washington, there will be
OL,17,Fsome modest operational adjustments to
OL,18,Fone or two royal engagements during
OL,19,Fthe trip, but the overall plan remains
OL,20,Fas previously outlined.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
