SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777546977
OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FSir Christian Turner, the British
OL,7,Fambassador to the US, said they were
OL,8,F"very confident that all appropriate
OL,9,Fsecurity measures are in place"
OL,10,Fregarding the royal visit.
OL,12,FThere have been other concerns around
OL,13,Fthe King's visit.
OL,15,FThe trip will not include meeting
OL,16,Fsurvivors of the disgraced paedophile
OL,17,FJeffrey Epstein, a decision taken "on
OL,18,Flegal advice", because of the
OL,19,Frequirement not to affect pending
OL,20,Fcourt cases, according to lawyers for
OL,21,FKing Charles III.
OL,26,@yD@cOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
