OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FOne survivor, Sharlene Rochard told
OL,7,FITV News, "(The King) should 100% meet
OL,8,Fwith survivors just on a human level.
OL,10,F"It's a human issue. This is not
OL,11,Fpolitical. This is literally just
OL,12,Fpeople. We are people. We are humans.
OL,13,FAnd if they care about humanity, then
OL,14,Fthey should care about survivors
OL,15,Feverywhere."
OL,17,FHere's what we know so far about the
OL,18,Fvisit.
OL,26,@oD@LpmoD@Upn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
