OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FThe President and First Lady greeted
OL,7,Fthe King and Queen when they arrived
OL,8,Fat the South Portico of the White
OL,9,FHouse on Monday afternoon.
OL,11,FAfter formal greetings and tea are
OL,12,Fcompleted, Charles and Camilla will
OL,13,Fjoin the President and First Lady for
OL,14,Fa tour of the newly expanded White
OL,15,FHouse Beehive, which is nestled on the
OL,16,FSouth Lawn near the White House
OL,17,FKitchen Garden.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
