OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FLater, the King and Queen will attend
OL,7,Fa garden party featuring guests
OL,8,Frepresenting the connection between
OL,9,Fthe US and UK.
OL,11,FThe royals will base themselves at
OL,12,FBlair House in Washington DC for the
OL,13,Fduration of their stay.
OL,15,FThe 120-room complex of four connected
OL,16,Fhouses is opposite the White House and
OL,17,Falso known as 'The President's Guest
OL,18,FHouse'.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
