OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FTrump and Melania will host a State
OL,7,FArrival Ceremony on the South Lawn of
OL,8,Fthe White House on Tuesday morning.
OL,10,FDrawing upon a tradition that dates
OL,11,Fback to the 18th century, the couple
OL,12,Fwill mark the official arrival of the
OL,13,Froyals with a traditional military
OL,14,Farrival ceremony, which includes
OL,15,Fmilitary honours by the US Army Herald
OL,16,FTrumpets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
