PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777546977
OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FNational anthems of both countries
OL,7,Fwill be played by "The President's
OL,8,FOwn" US Marine Band, with the
OL,9,FPresidential Salute Battery rendering
OL,10,Fa 21-gun cannon salute.
OL,12,FFollowing an Inspection of the Troops
OL,13,Fand a Troop in Review, facilitated by
OL,14,Fthe US Army Fife and Drum Corps, the
OL,15,Fpresident will then deliver remarks
OL,16,Ffrom the South Lawn.
OL,26,@oD@SOUpD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
