OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FAfterwards, both couples will proceed
OL,7,Fto the Blue Room Balcony, where they
OL,8,Fwill participate in a Pass in Review
OL,9,Fof 300 US Service Members and 500
OL,10,Fmembers of the US Armed Forces from
OL,11,Fall six military branches present at
OL,12,Fthe ceremony - a historic first for
OL,13,Fstate visits.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
