OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777546977
OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FThousands of guests will be gathered
OL,7,Fon the South Lawn, including Members
OL,8,Fof the President's Cabinet, Members of
OL,9,FCongress, the official Delegation of
OL,10,Fthe United States of America, the
OL,11,Fofficial Delegation of the UK,
OL,12,FAmerican military families and
OL,13,Fstudents from the British
OL,14,FInternational School of Washington.
OL,16,FThe King and Queen will then sign the
OL,17,FWhite House guest book and participate
OL,18,Fin an official gift exchange with the
OL,19,Fpresident and first lady in the Blue
OL,20,FRoom.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
