OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777546977
OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FWithin the spirit of Melania's
OL,7,FFostering the Future Together
OL,8,Finitiative, the small group, including
OL,9,Fseveral state champions from the
OL,10,FPresidential AI Challenge, will use
OL,11,Fvirtual reality headsets to learn
OL,12,Fabout the United Kingdom.
OL,14,FParticipants will also utilise AI-
OL,15,Fenabled glasses to learn about
OL,16,FAmerican history and the Special
OL,17,FRelationship by evaluating artefacts
OL,18,Ffrom the White House Collection and
OL,19,Fthe National Archives and Records
OL,20,FAdministration.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
