OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FOn Tuesday evening, Trump and Melania
OL,7,Fwill greet the royals upon their
OL,8,Farrival at the South Portico of the
OL,9,FWhite House for a State Dinner in the
OL,10,FEast Room.
OL,12,FThe Office of the First Lady will
OL,13,Fshare additional details on the State
OL,14,FDinner prior to the event.
OL,16,FCharles and Camilla will travel to New
OL,17,FYork on Wednesday, where they will
OL,18,Fattend the September 11 terrorist
OL,19,Fattack memorial.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777546977
OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FThe Queen will also give a specially
OL,7,Fmade toy of Winnie-the-Pooh character
OL,8,FRoo to the New York Public Library to
OL,9,Fcomplete a set of the beloved
OL,10,Fcharacters in one of the institution's
OL,11,Fcollections.
OL,13,FOn Thursday morning, Charles and
OL,14,FCamilla will return to the White House.
OL,16,FThe president and first lady will
OL,17,Fgreet them at the South Portico and
OL,18,Fsay their farewells in the Diplomatic
OL,19,FReception Room.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
