OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777546977
OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FAt the end of the trip, Charles will
OL,7,Ftravel solo to Bermuda for a three-day
OL,8,Froyal visit - his first to a British
OL,9,FOverseas Territory as King.
OL,11,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,12,Fweekly podcast about the Royal Family,
OL,13,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,14,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/18
